    "title": "Principal Frontend Developer at ECIL Holdings Services",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at ECIL Holdings Services. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Frontend Developer to strengthen our Kanpur-based team.\n\nAbout ECIL Holdings Services:\nECIL Holdings Services is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in Go\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n• Proficiency in Rust\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Flexible working hours\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Kanpur, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with ECIL Holdings Services!",
